Quickstrike:




With his head ducked, Quickstrike saw the instant the gernade hit the 
ground. His bright eyes went wide. He bolted to the side, trying to get away 
from it, but it blew up before he could get his distance. He was thrown to a 
tree, slamming his head and shoulder into the body of it. He went 
unconcious, slipping to the ground.
